>Coding Scheme Designator (0008,0102) R DCM IsRequiredRule / ValueRule
Input Information Sequence (0040,4021) R The Input Information Sequence (0040,4021) shall contain reference to a least the following items (additional items may be required for continuation procedures):
1. The RT Plan SOP Instance to be delivered. Its specified location shall be an OST Archive. Note that a specific product implementation could fulfill the roles of both a TMS and an OST Archive, in which case one AE Title could be used to retrieve all input SOP Instances for the UPS.
2. An RT Beams Delivery Instruction SOP Instance. Its specified location shall be the TMS.		 IsRequiredRule /
